    GridEdge
    A GridEdge connects two GridVertex.

    GridElement represents the abstract concept of an entity in the graph and specifies basic methods.

    Provides a unified way to construct a GridGraphManager for an application.

    Common exceptions to use with a GridGraphManager.

    A WsAndHttpChannelizer for use with GridGraphWsAndHttpChannelizer to support WS/HTTP connections.

    An implementation of the IoRegistry interface that provides serializers with custom configurations to support serialization of Grid Graph classes.

    An implementation of the IoRegistry interface that provides serializers with custom configurations to support serialization of Grid Graph classes.
    GridProperty<V>
    GridProperty is a Property connecting a vertex to a value.
